{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六章权力帮“火王”现身别传寺设下连环杀局。火王杀害大印法师并伪装其尸身设伏，梁斗识破陷阱接下剑王一剑。溪边假扮玉玺的火王对萧秋水和罗海牛施放火攻，两人被困阵势火海。萧秋水凭聪慧识破八阵图阵势，留下记号后成功带罗海牛脱险。雍希羽以水漫火之术扑灭大火，梁斗当众揭露其真实身份。权力帮炸毁后山封锁退路，众人决定死守别传寺。萧秋水把守海山门，以一人之力阻挡五名灰袍老者的闯关，大肚和尚及时赶到助战。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_yu_xi",
      "text": "“大师佛号玉玺？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xi",
      "speaker_name": "和尚",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "“阿弥陀佛。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_yu_xi",
      "text": "“有故人来了。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xi",
      "speaker_name": "和尚",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "“阿弥陀佛。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_yu_xi",
      "text": "“是梁大侠回来了。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "和尚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我要杀你。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这茶万万喝不得。”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“大印被杀，火王已至！”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "null",
      "speaker_name": "一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“大印法师已死？！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "null",
      "speaker_name": "一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是权力帮中八大天王的‘火工’么？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "null",
      "speaker_name": "一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“那么这人是谁？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“这杯茶……”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“秋水他——！”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这些人，真糟塌了我的好茶叶，我的好茶壶！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“快救火！”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hei",
      "speaker_name": "李黑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“用什么来救？！”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“幸好他们不在！他们在哪里？”",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“喂——萧兄弟——罗二哥——你——们——在——哪——里——？”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们在这里。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我们与罗小爷儿是拜把兄弟，你救了他命，就等于救了咱们，我要在此叩谢你的大恩！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“这些江湖好汉，礼俗不同朝臣，雍先生莫要见怪。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“你是指我迂腐，不了解武林中人的重义轻利，随时为朋友抛头颅、洒热血了？”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“雍兄，你要我说真话，还是说假话？”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“真话怎么说？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "胡福",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“假话又怎么说？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“真话就是雍学士不是雍学士，刚才一招以水漫火，天下间，不会多过三个人使得出来；”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我知道‘权力帮’有个‘水工’，但水工应不会破人工的火阵，”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“如果是说假话，那么雍学士就是雍学士，好茶道、爱读书的雍学士。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“萧兄弟呢？”",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "“我在这里，我在这里。”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他无大碍了。”",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“权力帮已炸毁后山，封锁了我们的退路，”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们现在只有两条路，一是投降，二是冲出去。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“还有第三条路。”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“什么路？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们不投降，也不冲出去，我们就留守在这里，与权力帮央一死战！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水、李黑、杀仔、大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“好！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“只不知你要留，还是要走？”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“你看我像留，还是像走？”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“你走不了。”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“你要强留？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“是权力帮留你。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "劳九",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“你究竟是谁？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "null",
      "speaker_name": "阿九",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“他究竟是谁？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "金刀胡福",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“权力帮现在还不攻击，是在等什么呢？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“等援兵，或等天黑——”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“现在我们踞海山门，只要从这边戍守，任何人过不了‘天梯铁镇’，易守难攻，但一到晚上……”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们就成了难守易攻了。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“也不见得易攻。权力帮之所以现在不攻，是想诱我们先攻，我们出击，他们在山问埋伏，一旦我们连这据点都失去，则退无死所了。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“那你不想突围了，困死在此？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“等。惟有等。对方要的是我们急躁，急躁只有送死，我们守在这里，至少还有安身之地。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“别传寺除后院有些蔬菜之外，鸡鸭泵大之类，一概绝灭，我们能撑到几时？权力帮人多势众，后援又至，你怎么办了还有，他们发起狠来放一把火烧，你又躲得过么？”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“雍兄不用担心，我们能等，急的反而是权力帮。权力帮若调得出后援，早就该来了，而且早就歼灭了我们。据情势看来，权力帮也正有大敌当前，拨不出入手来援，所以‘剑王’等才迟迟未发动。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“至于放火，有雍兄在，我们不怕。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们在五龙亭一役，打得十分轰动，广东武林，大概会传了出去，权力帮纵有后援，难道不怕我们也有救兵么？这一路来，我都留下了记号，权力帮与我们长期对峙，究竟不是善策。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“普天之下，敢与权力帮作对的，又有什么门派？！等他们来救，简直就是作梦！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“纵各大门派忌于权力帮人多势众，至少少林、武当二派，还是会仗义出手的。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“可惜远水救不了近火。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“但这里就有近水。长江三峡之总瓢把子，朱大天王的人，也向与权力帮不睦，说不定可以制住这所谓的‘天下第一帮’。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“当前之务，是先守好别传寺前后。以免背腹受敌，但得要保持紧密通讯，以免为敌所乘，更重要的是要守好前路唯一雨道：就是登霞关的海山门。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "null",
      "speaker_name": "广州十虎、萧秋水、大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“我等愿听梁大侠调度。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不能说调度，是合作防御。这里是我们的背水一战，再退，就没有路。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“依情形看来，权力帮人数实力虽占上风，但地利却不如我们，他们此刻不施硬攻，却用陷阱狙杀，想来兵力必相差不远，所以先困住我们：一是诱我们冲杀下山，自乱阵脚；二是制造气氛，迫使我们紧张，反生畏惧之情。所以我们应该轻松下来，沉着对敌。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“此说甚是。我们不但要自成联络网，还要在死守之时，创造反攻的契机，先消灭一两个主要敌人，可以减轻压力，取得胜机。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“现在于时已过，我们即刻就要开始布署。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "text": "“怎么？有没有动静？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“五位是——？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“什那小丑，也来挡路！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_zhe",
      "text": "“小心！”",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "null",
      "speaker_name": "一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“已通知梁大侠！”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6
    }
  ],
